

=Bio=

Graduated in Journalism from the State University of Rio de Janeiro (Uerj), has degree in Portuguese Language and is currently Master in Rural Federal University of Rio de Janeiro (UFRRJ). It is part of two collectives: the School of the  Rain Forest (www.escoladamataatlantica.org), where coordinates the Free Seeds House and also in i-Motiro, cultural association connected to  free software.                     Study the commons a few years ago, having helped in the translation into Portuguese of a text by David Bollier and writed for the book [[Copyfight]] ([http://www.copyfight.tk/])

